          font-weight: 500;
          font-size: 1.15em;
        ">${esc(a.content)}</td>
        <td class="confluenceTd" style="
          padding: 20px 16px;
          border-right: 1px solid #fdf2ef;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #fdf2ef;
          text-align: center;
